Types of Pensions
- Defined Benefit (DB)
  promise of a guaranteed future income one day like a salary
- Defined Contribution (DC)
  build up a pot of money
  
  - Personal Pension
    Stakeholder Pensions, SIPPs, Private Pensions
  - Workplace Pension
  
  
  
